{"tid":2440914,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"終於等到這一天！Red Velvet Wendy 有望 4 月隻身發片","createTime":"2021-03-10T09:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T10:13:33.000Z","uid":16659,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8b987d7c851851be5d4819d6f15bf0138cecdfdc","tid":2440914,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:50:17.000Z","msg":"許多 ReVeluv 盼望已久的事終於要實現了，期待 Wendy 的個人作品！<br />\n<br />\nSM Entertainment 今天（10 日）透露：「Wendy 正在製作個人專輯，目前的目標是於 4 月時發片，敬請多多期待。」<br />\n<br />\nRed Velvet 出道至今六年，直到去年才推出由瑟琪和 Irene 組成的小分隊，而身為主唱的 Wendy 則會是第一位隻身發片的成員，因此消息一曝光，立刻在網路上掀起熱烈迴響。<br />\n<br />\n儘管從來沒推出過個人專輯，但 Wendy 早已透過各種合作音源、OST、特別表演⋯⋯等展現令人印象深刻的實力和唱功。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uKzlyXIWrTY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuKzlyXIWrTY&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplWHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=11cecbd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uKzlyXIWrTY</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hMWK7oVvY-k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhMWK7oVvY-k&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplWHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=212b4123\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hMWK7oVvY-k</a>"},{"pid":"9a2ee1fd03f98e6a5d8e8263a87d6f8b409de39e","tid":2440914,"uid":255310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:51:05.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0aedc1a2a8498be8eab78a0b5540128a546b86c","tid":2440914,"uid":313222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:53:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6681011feebb7826a4060730324798cc71149eca","tid":2440914,"uid":93096,"like":0,"disli